## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-102"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> 類別是抽象 <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> 類別的具體實作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-102">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is a concrete implementation of the abstract <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> class.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-103"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類別是類似於 ASP.NET<xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is similar to the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-104"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類別具有許多屬性和方法的存取都很熟悉您，如果您已使用 ASP.NET 快取<xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-104">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has many properties and methods for accessing the cache that will be familiar to you if you have used the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-105">之間的主要差異<xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache>和<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類別是<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>讓它成為可用的已變更類別[!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]不是 ASP.NET 應用程式的應用程式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-105">The main differences between the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> and <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classes are that the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has been changed to make it usable by [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] applications that are not ASP.NET applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-106">例如，<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類別具有的任何相依性`System.Web`組件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-106">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has no dependencies on the `System.Web` assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-107">另一項差異是，您可以建立多個執行個體<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類別用於在相同的應用程式，而且在同一個<xref:System.AppDomain>執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-107">Another difference is that you can create multiple instances of the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class for use in the same application and in the same <xref:System.AppDomain> instance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-108"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類別不允許`null`為快取中的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-108">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class does not allow `null` as a value in the cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-109">任何嘗試新增或變更其值為快取項目`null`將會失敗。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-109">Any attempt to add or change a cache entry with a value of `null` will fail.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-110"><xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>類型未實作*快取區域*。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-110">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> type does not implement *cache regions*.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-111">因此，當您呼叫<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache>實作包含地區，參數的基底方法的方法不會傳遞參數的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-111">Therefore, when you call <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> methods that implement base methods that contain a parameter for regions, do not pass a value for the parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-112">使用所有區域參數的方法提供預設值`null`值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-112">The methods that use the region parameter all supply a default `null` value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-113">例如，<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法多載具有`regionName`參數的預設值是`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-113">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method overload has a `regionName` parameter whose default value is `null`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-114">下列範例會宣告預設的記憶體快取執行個體的參考。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-114">The following example declares a reference to the default memory cache instance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-115">快取項目使用<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy>物件，以提供快取項目的收回和到期的詳細資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-115">The cache entry uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy> object to provide eviction and expiration details for the cache entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79e9e-116">它也會使用<xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor>物件來監視檔案系統上的來源資料 （這是一個檔案） 的狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79e9e-116">It also uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor> object to monitor the state of the source data (which is a file) on the file system.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Private Sub btnGet_Click(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As EventArgs)   
    Dim cache As ObjectCache = MemoryCache.[Default]   
    Dim fileContents As String = TryCast(cache("filecontents"), String)   
  
    If fileContents Is Nothing Then   
        Dim policy As New CacheItemPolicy()   
        Dim filePaths As New List(Of String)()   
        filePaths.Add("c:\cache\example.txt")   
  
        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(New HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths))   
  
        ' Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents = File.ReadAllText("c:\cache\example.txt")   
  
        cache.[Set]("filecontents", fileContents, policy)   
    End If   
  
    Label1.Text = fileContents  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void btnGet_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)  
{  
    ObjectCache cache = MemoryCache.Default;  
    string fileContents = cache["filecontents"] as string;  
  
    if (fileContents == null)  
    {  
        CacheItemPolicy policy = new CacheItemPolicy();  
  
        List<string> filePaths = new List<string>();  
        filePaths.Add("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  
  
        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(new   
        HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths));  
  
        // Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents =   
            File.ReadAllText("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  
  
        cache.Set("filecontents", fileContents, policy);  
    }  
  
    Label1.Text = fileContents;  
}  
```
